--- !u!114 &826187731
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 826187728}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: dab40134f96b0c04e893ef68ca62f8c8, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::GameManager01
  dialogue_text01: {fileID: 1961642902}
  character_text01: {fileID: 726568880}
  dialogue01:
  - char_name: 
    dialogue_text: 
    options: []
  - char_name: characterText
    dialogue_text: I think I'm going to be sick-
    options: []
  - char_name: Time
    dialogue_text: Welcome to 400BCE, in what is now present-day India!
    options: []
  - char_name: characterText
    dialogue_text: This is a dream, this is a dream, this is a dream-
    options: []
  - char_name: Time
    dialogue_text: Well, whether you believe it or not, your date is arriving. Have
      fun.
    options: []
  - char_name: characterText
    dialogue_text: Wait, I STILL DON'T KNOW WHAT'S GOING ON-
    options: []
  - char_name: ???
    dialogue_text: Oh, I see the Gods have outdone themselves~
    options: []
  - char_name: 
    dialogue_text: 
    options: []
  - char_name: ???
    dialogue_text: And who might you be?
    options: []
  - char_name: characterText
    dialogue_text: Oh! Uh, my name is {playerName}.
    options: []
  - char_name: ???
    dialogue_text: I can't say I've heard that name before! Are you foreign?
    options: []
  - char_name: characterText
    dialogue_text: Something like that?
    options: []
  - char_name: Vikram
    dialogue_text: Well, I'm sure you already know me, the heir to the Daruwala family,
      Vikram. I don't mean to brag, but I am quite popular around here.
    options: []
  - char_name: characterText
    dialogue_text: ...
    options: []
  - char_name: Vikram
    dialogue_text: Cat got your tongue? I can't blame you~
    options: []
  - char_name: characterText
    dialogue_text: Sorry, uh, could I ask how you knew to meet me?
    options: []
  - char_name: Vikram
    dialogue_text: Hm? What do you mean? You wrote me QUITE the letter asking to
      meet me. Part of me was worried you'd be an obsessive fan.
    options: []
  - char_name: characterText
    dialogue_text: (I didn't write anything, but anyway)
    options: []
  - char_name: characterText
    dialogue_text: Oh, haha, no, not an obsessive fan, more so a, uh... journalist.
    options: []
  - char_name: Vikram
    dialogue_text: "Hm? I\u2019m not sure I believe you\u2026I don\u2019t think a
      journalist would\u2019ve written \r\nthe things you wrote to me~ "
    options: []
  - char_name: characterText
    dialogue_text: (What did Time write in that letter??)
    options: []
  - char_name: characterText
    dialogue_text: Oh...uh...
    options: []
  - char_name: Vikram
    dialogue_text: "Haha, you\u2019re adorable. Before I get carried away though\u2026 "
    options: []
  - char_name: 
    dialogue_text: ...
    options: []
  line_index01: 0
